  "texts": [
    "In human-machine collaboration, it's the human who empowers the chatbot, adding unique concepts and working on an idea with a machine in a loop.",
    "We agree with the point that using chatbots will drive human creative writing in another direction (Clark et al., 2018).",
    "However, we also consider that language models can boost the story concept creation if the peculiarities of the system are considered while working (Ippolito et al., 2022).",
    "This is confirmed by the results of our research, where the principles of generalization and clarifying questions were taken into account when creating story concepts.",
    "Ultimately, it's a human choice whether to use AI agents in creative writing and to what extent the output will be presented in the original work."
  ],
